sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant User as Seller browser
  participant SPA as apps/web SPA
  participant Auth as packages/auth
  participant Client as Supabase client
  participant Function as Edge Function
  participant DB as Supabase Postgres
  participant External as External provider

  User->>SPA: Open protected dashboard route
  SPA->>Auth: Restore session and profile
  Auth->>Client: getSession and load profile
  Client->>DB: Query profile, roles, plan through RLS
  DB-->>Client: User scoped data
  Auth-->>SPA: Auth state, role, plan, subscription
  SPA->>Function: Invoke domain API with bearer token
  Function->>Function: Parse request and validate auth/session
  Function->>DB: Read/write through anon or service role client
  alt Provider workflow
    Function->>External: Call marketplace, Stripe, AI, or email API
    External-->>Function: Provider response
  end
  DB-->>Function: Result
  Function-->>SPA: JSON response
  SPA-->>User: Update UI

